# Laravel 12 Spatie StarterKit - Cline AI Rules

## Project Overview
Professional Laravel 12 starter kit dengan React 19, TypeScript, Inertia.js, dan Spatie packages (Media, Permission, Activity Log). Real-time features menggunakan Laravel Reverb.

## Core Technologies
Backend: Laravel 12 | Frontend: React 19 + TypeScript 5.7 | UI: Tailwind CSS 4.0 + shadcn/ui | Real-time: Laravel Reverb

## Critical Patterns

### Page Structure (MANDATORY)
```tsx
import AppLayout from '@/layouts/app-layout';
import PageContainer from '@/components/page-container';
import Heading from '@/components/heading';

export default function Page() {
    return (
        <AppLayout breadcrumbs={breadcrumbs}>
            <Head title="Title" />
            <PageContainer maxWidth="4xl">
                <Heading title="Title" description="Desc" />
                {/* Content */}
            </PageContainer>
        </AppLayout>
    );
}
```

### PageContainer Widths
- `'none'` or `'full'` → Full width (tables)
- `'2xl'` → Simple forms
- `'4xl'` → Complex forms
- `'7xl'` → Galleries

## Code Rules

### DO:
✅ Use TypeScript interfaces for all props
✅ Use `@/` imports (never `../../`)
✅ Use existing shadcn/ui components (24 available)
✅ Use `PageContainer` for consistency
✅ Add permission checks (backend + frontend)
✅ Use `toast` for notifications
✅ Use `useForm` from Inertia
✅ Run formatters: `composer pint`, `npm run format`

### DON'T:
❌ Use `any` in TypeScript
❌ Create custom CSS (use Tailwind)
❌ Hardcode routes (use `route()`)
❌ Skip error handling
❌ Bypass permissions
❌ Forget loading states

## Available Components
Button, Input, Label, Textarea, Checkbox, Select, Card, Alert, Badge, Avatar, Dialog, Dropdown Menu, Sheet, Sidebar, Breadcrumb, Separator, Skeleton, Toggle, Tooltip, Table

## Common Patterns
- **DataTables**: `<DataTableWrapper ajax={{url: route('x.json')}} />`
- **Forms**: `const {data, setData, post, errors} = useForm({})`
- **Confirmation**: `const {openConfirmation} = useConfirmation()`
- **Permissions**: `{user.permissions.includes('edit-users') && <Button />}`

## File Locations
- Pages: `resources/js/pages/[Feature]/[Action].tsx`
- Components: `resources/js/components/`
- Types: `resources/js/types/`
- Layouts: `resources/js/layouts/`

## Naming
- Components: PascalCase (`AppSidebar.tsx`)
- Hooks/Utils: kebab-case (`use-appearance.tsx`)
- Routes: kebab-case (`/app-settings`)

